\v 11 Tuk nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e, ye n…®p…®g m…®fam yakarh…ôhuak tuk …ômi…ô m…ô Kughen tukr…ôvheik…®n-p…ôn …ômi…ô m…®m…ô n…®mraghien kap…ômi…ô in ratuatuk r…ômhen k…®n yame In r…®m…®rpen …ômi…ô tukun. K…®ni yakarh…ôhuak m…ô Kughen tukror wok ye n…ôsan…®nien kafan m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®gien huv…ô yame naksorkeikei m…ô taks…ôri-p…ôn, m…®ne wok huv…ô yam…ô m…®ne rams…®-p…ôn ye nhat…ôt…ôyen kap…ômi…ô, tukror kw…ônkwan.  
\v 12 K…®mas…®r yakarh…ôhuak m…ôkneik…®n m…ô jakrh…ôw…ôhsi-hakt…ô nhag Yesu Yermaru tuk nar…®mnar yame ramor ye n…®mraghien kap…ômi…ô, k…®ni In tukr…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ô …ômi…ô. Nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e tukru…ô ye n…®huv…ôyen kape Kughen kap…ôtaw…ô m…®ne Yesu Kristo Yermaru kap…ôtaw…ô.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yermam…ô yame ramor t…ôvhag…ô hah n…®p…®g m-fam  
\p
\v 1 Piak m…®n…ô m…®ne nowin…®k m…®n…ô. P…ôh yak…ôgkiar ye n…®p…®g yame Yesu Kristo Yermaru\f + \fr 2:1 \ft  ∆émru footnote ye 1 Tes 5:2.\f* kap…ôtaw…ô tukr…®rer…®g-p…ô m…®n iran, k…®ni Kughen tukrofug…®n …ôtaw…ô min Yesu Kristo.  
\v 2 Narmam…ô kamhani mham…ô k…®mas…®r y…®m…®rh…®ni profesi k…®rik u…ô y…®m…®rh…®rai n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®rik, m…®rh…®m…ô N…®p…®g kape Yermaru ruau…ô ta. M…ôr…®g, takhap…ôh n…®s…ôt…ôr…®g-p…®kien k…®n n…ôgkiarien a, mhap…ôh n…®sakur-akurien tukun. Neiku…ôyen en.  
\v 3-4 Takhap…ôh n…®seighanien k…®n yermam…ô k…®rik m…ô tukreiku…ô ir…ômi…ô k…®n n…ôgkiarien k…®rik, meinai n…®p…®g a tukr…®p…ôh n…®t…ôrhav-p…ôyen meriaji n…®p…®g yame narmam…ô tukhau…ô m…®sor t…®km…®r m…®n…ô kape Kughen m…®sarowag…®n k…®mi …ôri…ô m…®n…ô, k…®ni Kughen tukror …ôpu yermam…ô e kamni k…®m…ô ‚ÄòYermam…ô yame Ramor T…ôvhag…ô Hah N…®p…®g M…®fam.‚Äô\f + \fr 2:3-4 \ft P…ôh nien m…ô kw…ôn e in Setan, m…ôr…®g kwerm…®n k…®rik. Kamokr…ôn k…®n in k…®m…ô ‚Äòt…®km…®r kape Kristo‚Äô ye 1 Jon 2:18.\f* Ye n…®p…®g a narmam…ô tuks…ôhuak k…®mi kughen p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô, m…ôr…®g in tukror t…®km…®r k…®mi …ôri…ô, m…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ô atuk in rapita kughen m…®n…ô a. M…®v…ôn m…ôkw…ôt…ô ye Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen, mamni m…®m…ô in kughen. M…ôr…®g Kughen tukroriah …ôfrak…®s in r…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô kafan n…ôgkiarien kup…ôn.  
\v 5 ?Rhawor? ?N…®m…®s…ôruk…®n m…ô n…®p…®g y…®mnamar…ô k…®taw…ô-m k…®mi…ô y…®mnhajoun …ômi…ô k…®n nar…®mnar m…®n…ô e u…ô?  
\v 6 K…®ni nakw…ônharkun ta naha nhag…®n yame r…ôtap…®g k…®n kw…ôn a m…ô Kughen tukror …ôpu in ye n…®p…®g atuatuk kafan.  
\v 7 N…ôsan…®nien m…ôniw…ôn kape T…ôvhag…ô Hah Yame R…®mawor r…®nameriw…ôk-…ôrhav; m…ôr…®g yermam…ô yame r…ôtap…®g k…®n n…ôsan…®nien a, in tukror m…ôknak…®n meriaji Kughen tukr…®w…ôhsi-ta in.  
