\v 16 K…®ni p…ôh Yermaru kape n…ôm…ôrinuyen In p…®s…®n …ôm…ô tukr…®v…ôhsi-pre n…ôm…ôrinuyen n…®p…®g m…®fam ye norien m…®n…ô fam. P…ôh Yesu Yermaru tukramar…ô tuk …ômi…ô m…®fam.   
\p
\v 17 Yo Pol, yakv…ôh pen mamrai n…ôgkiarien e k…®n kwerm…®k, mamni-pre rhuv…ô tuk …ômi…ô. K…®ni ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô fam yakamrai m…ôkneik…®n m…ô takharkun m…ô in e in n…ôgkiarien kafak. In e in norien kape n…®raiyen kafak.   
\p
\v 18 P…ôh kap…ôtaw…ô Yermaru Yesu Kristo tukraut…ô-pre k…®n kafan n…®huv…ôyen k…®mi …ômi…ô m…®fam.   